Configuration from ME\\ 
Configuration from Gibbs\\
Configuration from Gibbs+ME+Gibbs
\item Plot 4: Evidence that Gibbs got stuck\\ 
x: iterations; \\
y: \\
Likelihood of Gibbs+ME+Gibbs
